reviewText: Brand new disc. Didn't work at all. Dud.

It can't just be me,but this is just horrible quality. I mean really bad. Almost unwatchable. I guess that's why its only 5.98. The starting menu looked nice and clear,but that's it...Ok ,it is better on a smaller screen, like a laptop,just can't watch it on a 55 inch TV. Movies themselves are decent. But then I am a Clara Bow fan,so Anything she is in,is good to me.
